Package: cbat4r
Type: Package
Title: Scaffold jsPsych Tasks in the CBAT Format
Version: 0.2.0
Authors@R: c(
    person(
      "Yoshihiko", "Kunisato",
      email = "ykunisato@psy.senshu-u.ac.jp",
      role = c("aut", "cre")
    )
  )
Description: Creates the directory layout and starter files to run 'jsPsych'
    experiments in the CBAT (Cognitive/Behavioral Assessment Tasks) format:
    HTML entry points for the Demo, JATOS and CEMA environments, init/run
    scripts, starter task code, and the official 'jsPsych' distribution
    (downloaded once per version and cached). Also generates Likert
    questionnaire and informed-consent tasks, Phaser 3 starters, and packages
    studies into JATOS '.jzip' archives.
License: MIT + file LICENSE
URL: https://github.com/cba-toolbox/cbat4r
BugReports: https://github.com/cba-toolbox/cbat4r/issues
Encoding: UTF-8
